1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 12=

3
00:01:00,719 --> 00:01:02,079
Is Your Majesty satisfied?

4
00:01:02,079 --> 00:01:02,960
Yes,

5
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:04,400
but it's not nearly enough.

6
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,040
I want to kill them

7
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,560
a thousand times over.

8
00:01:14,239 --> 00:01:15,560
I know

9
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,959
there's nothing

10
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:17,920
more satisfying than going back in time

11
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:20,159
to kill your enemies
with your own hands.

12
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,719
I will give you all of that.

13
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:24,560
The Holy Maiden of the Zhao Tribe

14
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,599
is truly extraordinary.

15
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:28,000
You've made me

16
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,879
grow even fonder of you.

17
00:01:35,519 --> 00:01:37,400
Where is the Holy Maiden?

18
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,159
My Lord,

19
00:01:38,159 --> 00:01:40,000
wasn't she executed?

20
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:46,760
These paintings,

21
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:47,879
you drew them, didn't you?

22
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,760
If you don't tell me,

23
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,519
I'll report to His Majesty

24
00:01:54,519 --> 00:01:55,879
that you've been harboring

25
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:57,439
a foreign maidservant.

26
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,280
How did you know?

27
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:00,760
Are you going to talk?

28
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,480
Where is she?

29
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,159
His Majesty...

30
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:08,560
His Majesty ordered the swap.

31
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:09,439
My Lord!

32
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,400
Mercy, My Lord!

33
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,080
My Lord!

34
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:11,759
My Lord!

35
00:02:11,759 --> 00:02:13,520
Mercy, My Lord!

36
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,439
My Lord!

37
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:16,240
Mercy, My Lord!

38
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:51,800
Your Majesty.

39
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,319
Minister Li has a report.

40
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,159
Get out!

41
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,120
What is it, Your Majesty?

42
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,000
The dream I just had

43
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:05,960
is quite interesting.

44
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:12,960
Consort Rong,

45
00:03:13,319 --> 00:03:14,759
word has spread through the palace

46
00:03:14,919 --> 00:03:16,840
that His Majesty hasn't held court
for days.

47
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,719
I wonder

48
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:19,120
who's in the Palace of Punishment?

49
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,360
Who else?

50
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:23,319
Whoever's been missing
from the palace lately.

51
00:03:23,319 --> 00:03:24,400
That's who.

52
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:25,439
Consort Rong,

53
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:27,120
are you truly letting this go?

54
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,879
Tonight, Your Majesty,

55
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:35,840
how do you want to kill them?

56
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:43,719
Not tonight.

57
00:03:43,719 --> 00:03:44,919
Tonight,

58
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,520
I want you.

59
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:54,759
You dare stop me?

60
00:03:54,759 --> 00:03:55,879
I'm going in anyway.

61
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:56,599
His Majesty said

62
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,719
no one is to enter.

63
00:03:58,439 --> 00:03:59,479
I am the Consort.

64
00:03:59,479 --> 00:04:00,319
Do you dare stop me?

65
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:03,960
Out of my way.

66
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,360
Zhaohua.

67
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,000
Why are you here?

68
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,039
Your Majesty.

69
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:10,919
I had a nightmare.

70
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:12,759
I dreamt of the day my brother died.

71
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,479
I was so scared.

72
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:17,279
When I woke and you weren't beside me,

73
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,240
I was even more afraid.

74
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,879
Don't be afraid, Zhaohua.

75
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,000
I'm here.

76
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:24,399
But you haven't come to see me

77
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:26,000
in days.

78
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,319
I thought

79
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:30,040
perhaps you'd found someone new

80
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,759
and no longer wanted me.

81
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:32,680
How could that be?

82
00:04:33,279 --> 00:04:34,800
In my heart,

83
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,480
you will always be first.

84
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,519
Is that true?

85
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,959
Absolutely.

86
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:46,120
What is it that I can't see?

87
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,079
Look.

88
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:55,519
I told you there's no one here.

89
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:56,839
You wouldn't believe me.

90
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,319
So it seems

91
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:07,079
I misjudged you.

92
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:09,600
It's my fault for neglecting you.

93
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,439
Then, tonight,

94
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:16,079
let Zhaohua keep you company.

95
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:17,560
Good.

96
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:29,720
Let go.

97
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,079
Let me go!

98
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,040
Let me go!

99
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:34,800
Let go!

100
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:37,759
Let go!

101
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,519
(I should have known.)

102
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,720
(His Majesty had his eye on Yukui
all along.)

103
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:58,600
(He had it all planned out.)

104
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:01,959
(He was waiting for Rong Zhaohua
to calm down,)

105
00:06:02,879 --> 00:06:05,079
(then pull off a switch.)

106
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:06,199
(This complicates things.)

107
00:06:07,079 --> 00:06:07,920
(We don't even know)

108
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,279
(where she is right now.)

109
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:11,560
(There may still be a way.)

110
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:15,240
(Officially speaking,)

111
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,720
(Jiang Yukui is already dead.)

112
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,480
(If I expose the truth now,)

113
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:21,439
(it would undermine
His Majesty's authority.)

114
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:24,439
(Consort Rong.)

115
00:06:24,439 --> 00:06:25,279
(Lord Nine-Thousand is here.)

116
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,920
(Why are you here?)

117
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,680
(I came to give you some information.)

118
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:42,000
(How did you know)

119
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:45,079
(that Jiang Yukui is in the inner
chamber of the Palace of Punishment?)

120
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:47,319
(When I want to know something,)

121
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:48,839
(I have my ways.)

122
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:51,639
(I came today to ask)

123
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,759
(for your assistance.)

124
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:57,600
(To be allowed into the inner chamber)

125
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,879
(means His Majesty holds you dear.)

126
00:06:59,879 --> 00:07:01,519
(Now that Jiang Yukui is dead)

127
00:07:01,519 --> 00:07:02,839
(in the eyes of the world,)

128
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:05,319
(you're putting me
in a difficult position.)

129
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:07,160
(That's precisely why you should help.)

130
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:09,120
(Back then,)

131
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,120
(when His Majesty)

132
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:12,040
(was solely devoted to Jiang Yusang,)

133
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:14,000
(you fell out of favor.)

134
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,480
(You wouldn't want)

135
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,600
(a repeat of that,)

136
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,920
(would you?)

137
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,680
(On the surface, you're helping me.)

138
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,360
(In truth, you're helping yourself.)

139
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,079
(Fine.)

140
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:26,920
(Then let me)

141
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,519
(toast to our cooperation)

142
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,959
(with tea instead of wine.)

143
00:07:31,639 --> 00:07:32,800
(To mutual benefit.)

144
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,360
(You're carrying
the Emperor's child now.)

145
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,639
(No matter what,)

146
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,720
(His Majesty will consider
your feelings.)

147
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,600
(And since Jiang Yukui
is officially dead,)

148
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,160
(His Majesty wouldn't want her)

149
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,560
(to be seen in public anyway.)

150
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,839
Why did you stop me?

151
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:59,319
I was one step away,

152
00:07:59,839 --> 00:08:00,480
just one step

153
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,160
from killing Zhu Yunqi

154
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,399
and avenging my sister!

155
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:04,839
And then?

156
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,519
What do you mean?

157
00:08:09,759 --> 00:08:10,959
What's your next move?

158
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:12,199
What about your own safety?

159
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,199
You had no plan.

160
00:08:13,199 --> 00:08:14,519
You wanted to do it all alone,

161
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:15,399
inside the Palace of Punishment,

162
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,680
assassinate the sovereign?

163
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:18,480
Tell me.

164
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,160
How many people
can your Divine Power control?

165
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,360
How were you going to escape?

166
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,560
Then I'll die!

167
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:26,040
For as long as I can remember,

168
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,360
besides my sister,

169
00:08:27,879 --> 00:08:29,399
no one has ever cared about me.

170
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,439
I just want to avenge her.

171
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:31,519
I care!

172
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:35,580
♪The moon sinks in the west.
The cold lamp burns low♪

173
00:08:35,780 --> 00:08:38,900
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

174
00:08:39,220 --> 00:08:43,020
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

175
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,759
I care.

176
00:08:49,580 --> 00:08:52,980
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

177
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,320
I care.

178
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,120
I don't want to see you in danger.

179
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,480
I don't want to see you hurt.

180
00:09:05,159 --> 00:09:06,519
And I don't want to see you

181
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:08,159
risking your life again and again

182
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:10,120
in pursuit of revenge.

183
00:09:11,820 --> 00:09:14,980
♪The green lamp sheds no light
upon one who entered the path♪

184
00:09:14,980 --> 00:09:18,180
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

185
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:20,159
Yukui.

186
00:09:21,039 --> 00:09:21,720
Feng Ye.

187
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:25,220
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

188
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,960
Actually, I...

189
00:09:31,559 --> 00:09:32,159
Feng Ye.

190
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:34,960
Feng Ye.

191
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:39,000
You've threatened me time and again.

192
00:09:40,279 --> 00:09:42,399
Now you'll taste

193
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,399
my power.

194
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:47,320
(I came today to ask)

195
00:09:47,679 --> 00:09:49,519
(for your assistance.)

196
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,000
Holy Maiden,

197
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,559
how is My Lord?

198
00:10:12,559 --> 00:10:13,200
The poison,

199
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,399
has it subsided?

200
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:15,600
Don't worry.

201
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,559
He should wake up soon.

202
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:18,919
Good.

203
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:19,679
Good.

204
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,960
Here, My Lord.

205
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:23,360
Holy Maiden, wait.

206
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,440
Holy Maiden,

207
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:28,840
could I trouble you

208
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,679
to look after My Lord?

209
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:34,759
Why?

210
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,320
You may all leave.

211
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:37,679
Yes.

212
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,279
Holy Maiden.

213
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:45,360
I think

214
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,080
if My Lord wakes up

215
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,480
and sees you here,

216
00:10:48,799 --> 00:10:50,000
he'll be overjoyed.

217
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:54,080
You may not know this,

218
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,360
but My Lord

219
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,399
cares deeply about you.

220
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:57,919
Before this,

221
00:10:57,919 --> 00:10:59,279
when he wanted to cheer you up,

222
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,399
he actually asked me

223
00:11:00,399 --> 00:11:01,879
how to make a woman happy.

224
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,480
How would I know?

225
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:05,639
So I just said something offhand.

226
00:11:05,639 --> 00:11:06,840
I never thought

227
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:07,960
My Lord

228
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,080
would take it seriously.

229
00:11:09,759 --> 00:11:10,639
(I had Feng Liu prepare)

230
00:11:10,639 --> 00:11:12,240
(all these gold and silver ornaments
for you.)

231
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,440
(They're all yours.)

232
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:18,360
(I had the servants build this birdcage)

233
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,600
(and leave this window open.)

234
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:21,600
(I was thinking of giving it)

235
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:23,600
(a designated spot.)

236
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,480
So back then,

237
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,639
he was trying to cheer me up.

238
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,320
Holy Maiden.

239
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,559
You may think

240
00:11:34,559 --> 00:11:36,919
My Lord ruined your plan,

241
00:11:37,399 --> 00:11:38,360
but truly,

242
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,240
in his heart,

243
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:44,240
what he cares about most is your safety.

244
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,759
My safety?

245
00:11:58,799 --> 00:11:59,279
Please,

246
00:11:59,279 --> 00:12:00,000
Holy Maiden.

247
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,679
You're awake.

248
00:12:22,679 --> 00:12:23,840
Just now, Feng Liu and I

249
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,120
were so worried about you.

250
00:13:12,940 --> 00:13:14,340
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

251
00:13:14,820 --> 00:13:16,260
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

252
00:13:16,460 --> 00:13:19,580
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

253
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:23,700
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

254
00:13:26,660 --> 00:13:28,380
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

255
00:13:28,380 --> 00:13:29,900
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

256
00:13:30,260 --> 00:13:33,660
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

257
00:13:33,660 --> 00:13:37,660
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

258
00:13:38,820 --> 00:13:41,980
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

259
00:13:41,980 --> 00:13:45,540
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

260
00:13:45,540 --> 00:13:47,860
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

261
00:13:47,860 --> 00:13:52,060
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

262
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:54,140
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

263
00:13:54,140 --> 00:13:55,660
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

264
00:13:55,660 --> 00:13:58,860
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

265
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:01,180
♪In dreams, it's you♪

266
00:14:01,180 --> 00:14:02,580
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

267
00:14:02,580 --> 00:14:05,900
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

268
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:09,300
♪I can't forget the stars in your eyes♪

269
00:14:09,300 --> 00:14:12,860
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

270
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:16,100
♪In this mortal world, there is only us♪

271
00:14:16,100 --> 00:14:19,540
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
